This paper is related to natural language processing and machine learning, which are covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) since the paper proposes a method to improve the performance of a model for machine translation and speech recognition. The second likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) since the paper deals with the initialization method of a neural network model. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) since the paper is related to the development of intelligent systems for language processing. The fourth likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) since the paper proposes a method to improve the performance of a neural network model. The fifth likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) since the paper deals with the processing of sequential data, which is also relevant to image and video processing.
